{"body": "This will not work. `tr` does not work like `gsub` when the to_str is longer than the from_str. See\r\n\r\nFor example:\r\n\r\n```\r\n> \"yo  dawg\".tr(\"  \", \"&nbsp; \")\r\n => \"yonndawg\"\r\n\r\n> \"yo  dawg\".gsub(\"  \", \"&nbsp; \")\r\n => \"yo&nbsp; dawg\"\r\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/14464827", "created_at": "2013-03-05T20:59:02Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/9564#issuecomment-14464827", "updated_at": "2013-03-05T20:59:02Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 9564, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teeparham/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teeparham/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teeparham/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/teeparham", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teeparham/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/teeparham", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teeparham/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/5cb2a77d7fa96c122da085edc4dcbe42?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F349fda3c9d90de7e62c9ada6c0550a8b.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teeparham/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teeparham/received_events", "gravatar_id": "5cb2a77d7fa96c122da085edc4dcbe42", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teeparham/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "teeparham", "type": "User", "id": 54017, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/teeparham/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523d1c55bd354364b9004c3c"}, "id": 14464827, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/9564"}
